    "description": "After the last human war, gases were spread through the atmosphere making it unbreathable. <br />\r\nThe richest fled to orbital colonies and the others took refuge underground.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou are a young hothead, hired by a team of scientists left on earth who are looking for a solution to bring humans back to the surface.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGet ready to fight giant Insects for the future of humanity !<br />\r\nPlayable from 1 to 4 players, Hexapoda is inspired by arcade classics.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- 4 game modes : Normal , Hard , Manic and Boss Rush!<br />\r\n- Unlock 3 Different endings, new features and new items..<br />\r\n- 12 stages, 4 futuristic combat aircrafts with their own style of shooting, <br />\r\n- Complete the bestiary inspired by existing insects,<br />\r\n- Unlock all the 35 Achievements,<br />\r\n- Online Leaderboards for each difficulty.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEnjoy the original epic soundtrack composed by the french electronic music band Double Dragon!",
